==Useful Info==
'''Xak'krixis''' is a [[unique]] [[formicid]] who has a dangerous set of spells and spawns with a [[venom]]-branded two-handed weapon and a shield. Also, Xak'krixis can [[dig]] walls while pursuing the player or running away.

